--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: b48b7ed3e5647da4191288c45520b384, type: 3}
  m_Name: 0_DialogStart
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Game.Dialog.DialogData
  dialogId: 0_DialogStart
  lines:
  - speakerName: Aira
    text: "Okay. The coordinates from that radio static pointed here. \nIf there's
      anyone left... if that settlement is real...  "
  - speakerName: Aira
    text: "it has to be up at the summit. \n(Taking a shaky breath, rubbing her arms
      against the chill) "
  - speakerName: Aira
    text: 'I just need to find a sign. A trail marker, a <b><color=#ffff00>Campfire</color></b>,
      a piece of trash.

      Anything human. '
  - speakerName: Aira
    text: "I can't be the only one who made it out of that place. \nMaybe i need
      to find high place like <b><color=#ffff00>Light House</color></b> (Voice low,
      trying to reassure)"
  - speakerName: Aira
    text: 'Something''s wrong with this place, though. It''s too quiet. And the map... '
  - speakerName: Aira
    text: "the map says this grove shouldn't even be here. \n(Voice dropping to a
      nervous whisper)"
  - speakerName: Aira
    text: "The trunks... it almost looks like they're leaning toward the path. \nLike
      they're listening to me breathe. (A slight tremor voice)"
  - speakerName: Aira
    text: "Stop it. You're just exhausted. Just keep moving. \nFind the survivors.
      And whatever you do... "
  - speakerName: Aira
    text: "don't stay in the shade too long. \n(Shaking off the fear, voice firming
      up)"
